{"tid":1337831,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"條線拉到好長，好分散，就一定要到到都夠多人！","createTime":"2019-07-21T11:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T11:26:21.000Z","uid":82955,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f819442428dcd1b18b93979bfca0f6741f64ec","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"要去邊，有好多意見。好多唔同論述。<br />\n大家唔再集中係一個位，無錯每個位人數都會分薄左，但記得，對面玩家都會被拉散。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣可能做到真正既Be Water，但重點係，每個位都要夠人！<br />\n只要夠人，被拉薄既就唔係我地隊，係人地隊。<br />\n<br />\n條線拉到好長，好分散，就一定要到到都夠多人！<br />\n不散。平安。"},{"pid":"93099822a37b54e8d1286a4a0b0efa1dff9ee5aa","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"Wherever we are, We stand together as one."},{"pid":"c35cd04ead5d9f158e9afa11ecc560c9cf76ef44","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:08:06.000Z","msg":"Wherever we are, We stand together as one."},{"pid":"ca6fc2795828f985fd190edc95f089b554c4e8d0","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"Wherever we are, We stand together as one."},{"pid":"1d1aaa918549196530db9af1b6bb8d0483c13706","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"Wherever we are, We stand together as one."},{"pid":"45d0271bf7d5fe0b94b0779526785e13baa3ab74","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"Wherever we are, We stand together as one."},{"pid":"8f5d685f3cbd6812d7d03fc65a1ee4763fe4cc9d","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"Wherever we are, We stand together as one."},{"pid":"ce471219f4f368e3e8976e4b71f83d7a8e1c71d4","tid":1337831,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T11:10:36.000Z","msg":"Wherev